# LaTeX build artifacts - regenerated every time you compile, so no need
# to track them in git. Confirmed by an actual test compile of report.tex.
*.aux
*.bbl
*.blg
*.fdb_latexmk
*.fls
*.log
*.out
*.synctex.gz
*.toc

# The compiled PDF itself - a GitHub Actions workflow builds this
# automatically on every push and makes it downloadable, so there's no
# need to commit it here too (and it'd just cause noisy diffs on every
# edit). Remove this line if you'd rather commit the PDF directly instead.
report.pdf
